[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    584[0m:[38;5;10m[49m - **Recipe 8.5 (Problem List Extraction):** Provides the entity extraction foundation for identifying diagnoses in notes
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    585[0m:[38;5;10m[49m - **Recipe 8.8 (Clinical Assertion Classification):** Handles the present/absent/possible/family determination critical for phenotype accuracy
